{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "库鲁西遗迹",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "爱莎",
            "context": "拉碧丝小姐，怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "遗迹里面我大致调查了一遍，\\n没有发现类似宝物的东西。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "应该是有什么暗门吧。\\n为了打开那个暗门，\\n才需要你们一族手上的钥匙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "爱莎",
            "context": "钥匙……到底是什么呢？\\n我并没有从父亲那里\\n拿到过那种东西……呀啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "只是一只老鼠而已。\\n它跑到墙壁的裂缝里去了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "难道说，这面墙……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "爱莎",
            "context": "拉碧丝小姐，怎么了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "墙的另一面似乎是空的……\\n而且墙上还有不自然的凹陷。\\n这个凹陷的形状，就像是手……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "！\\n爱莎，你能摸一下这个凹陷吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "爱莎",
            "context": "好、好的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "人声",
            "context": "正在解析生物体信息……\\n已确认权限要素，进行解锁。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "爱莎",
            "context": "墙壁竟然移动了！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "看来继承了族人血统的人\\n本身就是钥匙呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "好了，我们继续向前吧。\\n真期待会有什么宝物\\n在等着我们呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "爱莎",
            "context": "这是，什么啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "我见过帝国的人用，\\n好像是古代的魔导兵器吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "爱莎",
            "context": "兵器……这就是宝物吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "这有一块石板。\\n上面写着古代文字呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "爱莎",
            "context": "写了什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "这个古代遗迹\\n似乎是1000年前的研究所……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "曾在这里进行的是给既有兵器\\n添加特殊功能的研究。\\n那个魔导兵器似乎就是研究成果。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "守护石",
            "context": "咯咯咯……已确认有权限者的\\n生物信息。自动重启……\\n重新开始实验。主管，请下命令。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "爱莎",
            "context": "开、开口说话了！？\\n不对，它叫我主管？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "可能是因为你父亲的祖先\\n曾经是这个研究的负责人吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "守护石",
            "context": "请下战斗命令。战斗命令，\\n战斗命令，战斗命令，命令，命令，\\n命令命令命令命令命命命命命……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "爱莎",
            "context": "它、它好像不太对劲啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "拉碧丝，终于找到你了！\\n等等……这是啥！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这是守护石！\\n为什么会在这种地方？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "是圣城的王子他们！\\n一路追到这里来了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "守护石",
            "context": "未能获取命令……\\n改为自自、自动战斗、模式。\\n检测到的生物、全部、消除。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "竟然……消失了！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呃！？刚才的攻击，\\n是从哪里发出的！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "爱莎",
            "context": "呀啊啊啊！？\\n到底发生什么了！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "这攻击，难道是……\\n我要放烟雾弹了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂，快看！\\n烟雾里有影子浮现！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那个形状，\\n是刚才的守护石吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "守护石",
            "context": "咯咯咯……视线模糊。视线模糊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "趁它找不到我们的时候，\\n赶快藏起来吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "本以为它已经消失了，\\n却突然发动攻击……\\n那块守护石到底是什么啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "它是经过改造的，\\n追加了通过折射光线\\n融入周围风景掩护自己的功能。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那种事，为什么你会知道？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "石板上写的。这个先不说，\\n它因为年久失修正处于失控状态，\\n会不分敌我进行攻击。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "要是它跑到遗迹外面去就糟了。\\n得想办法阻止它才行。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "可是，我们要怎么\\n和会隐身的敌人战斗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "就像刚才那样用烟雾\\n来让它现形怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "刚才那是我最后一个烟雾弹了。\\n不过，我有一个作战计划。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "首先，王子殿下你们负责当诱饵，\\n牵制住敌人的攻击，\\n我趁机确认它发动攻击的方向。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "确定敌人位置之后，\\n我用铳来射击。怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "你说的作战计划也许可行。\\n不过，我们怎么知道你会不会\\n趁我们牵制住它的时候逃跑啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "爱莎",
            "context": "你是说拉碧丝小姐\\n会丢下我们不管吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "这家伙可是偷别人东西的罪犯。\\n不能轻易相信她。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "你怀疑我是应该的。\\n我也绝对不会要求你相信我。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "但是，你想一下好吗？\\n现在怎么做才是上上策。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "兰扎卜，我们就按她说的做吧……\\n这样比我们光靠自己战斗\\n更有胜算。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "万一拉碧丝逃跑了，\\n我们再靠自己的力量就好。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "真没办法……\\n她要是叛变了我可不管。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "谢谢你们两位。\\n那我们就开始作战吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂，蠢货！\\n我们来当你的对手！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好，上钩了！\\n照这个架势躲避它的攻击！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "敌人是一边移动一边攻击的，\\n会很难瞄准。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "嗯！？没击中的攻击\\n击碎了墙壁，瓦砾都……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "拉碧丝！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "可恶！都怪尘土，\\n没法确认拉碧丝有没有事！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "尘土……对了！\\n我们攻击墙壁，让尘土飞扬！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "看到了，就在那里！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呃！太浅了吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "尘土要消散了！\\n又要看不到它了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我盯上的猎物跑不了。\\n再见了，破铜烂铁先生。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "守护石倒下了！\\n刚才的攻击是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "我的铳法怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "拉碧丝，原来你没事啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "躲避掉下来的瓦砾，\\n简直小菜一碟。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "不过王子殿下，\\n你竟然能靠尘土找出\\n敌人的位置，挺机灵的嘛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这只是我一心杀敌\\n偶然想到的办法。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "能想到这一点就证明你本身很聪明。\\n而且你还有接受我的计划的判断能力，\\n最重要的是你浑身充满了正义感。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拉碧丝",
            "context": "如果是被你这样的人抓住，\\n或许也不错吧……说笑的♪",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}